 FormatShield requires libmelf. To build and install libmelf, cd in lib/libmelf directory, and
 ./configure
 make
 make install				(to be done as root)
 
 
To build the formatshield:
	make

To generate debugging info:
	make debug
	
Installation:
	make install			(to be done as root)


The makefile will only copy the library and man page to the appropriate
directories. It also gives an option to install formatshield on a system-wide basis. 
To activate formatshield only for the current user, define an environment 
variable LD_PRELOAD=/lib/libfshield.so





